{"tid":384394,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港人用原子筆為台灣麻雀做人工呼吸，醫生：有感染禽流感風險","createTime":"2017-09-02T09:12:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-02T15:20:39.000Z","uid":24282,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1d90369cdd2df467cbf2872bf2ca43ca035acc01","tid":384394,"uid":24282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T09:12:58.000Z","msg":"據有關專頁帖文資料指，當時事主一家人正前往（台灣）某科學博物館，見到有麻雀倒地不醒，經檢查後發現喉嚨有堵塞物，麻雀全身發軟沒有反應。<br />\n事主的太太從隨身「八寶袋」內掏出一支原子筆，把原子筆拆出彈簧，鑽入麻雀口腔位置，成功取出阻塞物，但小麻雀的呼吸依然微弱，該名男子決定為麻雀進行「人工呼吸」，成功拯救小鳥！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/my903/videos/10155206991058558/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmy903%2Fvideos%2F10155206991058558%2F&d=RYzsNvr9Civu4n4MXYouBsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=c6a8f995\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/my903/videos/10155206991058558/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fad74e29153c505135f6a97472b9016a5f82eec0","tid":384394,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T09:16:47.000Z","msg":"新變種病毒<br />\nGogogo"},{"pid":"83556a6805d25b3ff98fabf4fa5235bd501f8406","tid":384394,"uid":49004,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T09:23:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4adc41e6595804b119fc39358e3cb39c79022e22","tid":384394,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor